column1: # Please refer to 10.5281/zenodo.5525214 for details on
# the dataset and the link to the publication!
# As the article has not yet been peer-reviewed
# Electron drift velocity from data using (internal) 83mKr deacays in the
# HeXe setup. Errors include systematic uncertainties! Velocity given in mm/micro second
# And field values in kV/cm. LXe temperature: (173.41 +/- 0.11) K.
# Correspondence can be directed to Florian Joerg (fjoerg@mpi-hd.mpg.de)
